{
  "id": "5b9cd0f00a4b690013c6d690",
  "title": "OKR(書籍)",
  "created": 1537003775,
  "updated": 1547049333,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5b9cd0f00a4b690013c6d690",
      "text": "OKR(書籍)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537003775,
      "updated": 1542022617
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd101aff09e00007aad1e",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/0caa95e3dd98b0c6061393d05ee65d45]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537003778,
      "updated": 1537003778
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd118aff09e00007aad20",
      "text": "\t[OKR] シリコンバレー式で大胆な目標を達成する方法",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537003801,
      "updated": 1542022622
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd156aff09e00007aad21",
      "text": " \tもう、こういうタイトルを見ると「また原典と全然違うタイトルつけてるのでは」って疑いが湧くようになってしまった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537003862,
      "updated": 1545899500
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd181aff09e00007aad22",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/e6467cee240bdfbbc88e4ad087620d1d]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537003905,
      "updated": 1537003927
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd197aff09e00007aad23",
      "text": "\t\t[Radical Focus] - Achieving Your Most Important Goals with Objectives and Key Results",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537003927,
      "updated": 1542024040
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd25baff09e00007aad24",
      "text": "  \"Radical Focus\"とは何か？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537004124,
      "updated": 1542025331
    },
    {
      "id": "5c361971aff09e0000c90deb",
      "text": " [クリスティーナ・ウォドキー]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1547049329,
      "updated": 1547049333
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd0ffaff09e00007aad1d",
      "text": "\t[Amazon https://amzn.to/2QxVwzZ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537003775,
      "updated": 1537003793
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd31daff09e00007aad25",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537004317,
      "updated": 1537004317
    },
    {
      "id": "5c248e95aff09e0000e8fc85",
      "text": "\tストーリー仕立てにしてあるタイプのビジネス書、第1部がストーリー、第2部がフレームワークの解説",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545899669,
      "updated": 1545899747
    },
    {
      "id": "5c248ee3aff09e0000e8fc86",
      "text": "\tOKRに興味を持った[nishio.icon]に、オススメされたのはこちらの本ではなく、GoogleにOKRを導入した本人が書いた[Measure What Matters]だった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545899747,
      "updated": 1545900283
    },
    {
      "id": "5c2490fbaff09e0000e8fc95",
      "text": "\t確かにストーリー仕立てなのは何を言いたいのかよくわからんなぁという感想",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545900283,
      "updated": 1545900297
    },
    {
      "id": "5c2490cdaff09e0000e8fc93",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545900238,
      "updated": 1545900238
    },
    {
      "id": "5c2490cdaff09e0000e8fc94",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545900238,
      "updated": 1545900238
    },
    {
      "id": "5c248ee3aff09e0000e8fc87",
      "text": "\tやり遂げることができない5つの理由(p.128)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545899747,
      "updated": 1545899793
    },
    {
      "id": "5c248eebaff09e0000e8fc88",
      "text": "\t\tゴールに優先順位をつけていない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545899755,
      "updated": 1545899770
    },
    {
      "id": "5c248efaaff09e0000e8fc89",
      "text": "\t\t熱意をもってもれなくゴールを伝えていない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545899770,
      "updated": 1545899783
    },
    {
      "id": "5c248f07aff09e0000e8fc8a",
      "text": "\t\tやり遂げるためのプランがない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545899783,
      "updated": 1545899801
    },
    {
      "id": "5c248f19aff09e0000e8fc8b",
      "text": "\t\t重要事項のための時間を設けていない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545899802,
      "updated": 1545899812
    },
    {
      "id": "5c248f24aff09e0000e8fc8c",
      "text": "\t\t繰り返さずに辞めてしまう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545899812,
      "updated": 1545899983
    },
    {
      "id": "5c248fe6aff09e0000e8fc8d",
      "text": "\tOのルール",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545900006,
      "updated": 1545900012
    },
    {
      "id": "5c248fecaff09e0000e8fc8e",
      "text": "\t\t定性的で人を鼓舞する内容にする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545900012,
      "updated": 1545900031
    },
    {
      "id": "5c249031aff09e0000e8fc92",
      "text": "\t\t\t定量的にしない。「素晴らしい成果」などの曖昧な表現をする→それを計測する手段はKR",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545900081,
      "updated": 1545900097
    },
    {
      "id": "5c248fffaff09e0000e8fc8f",
      "text": "\t\t時間的な縛りを作る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545900031,
      "updated": 1545900041
    },
    {
      "id": "5c249004aff09e0000e8fc90",
      "text": "\t\t各チームが独立して実行できるようにする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545900036,
      "updated": 1545900051
    },
    {
      "id": "5c249013aff09e0000e8fc91",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545900051,
      "updated": 1545900080
    },
    {
      "id": "5c248e91aff09e0000e8fc84",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545899666,
      "updated": 1545899666
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd31daff09e00007aad26",
      "text": "\tインテルが[ドラッカー]のMBO（[Management by Objectvies]）を取り入れる際に当時のCEOがアレンジして生まれた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537004318,
      "updated": 1537004342
    },
    {
      "id": "5c248e21aff09e0000e8fc82",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1545899554,
      "updated": 1545899554
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd41eaff09e00007aad2a",
      "text": " [及川 卓也]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537004574,
      "updated": 1537004971
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd5abaff09e00007aad35",
      "text": " \t[src https://swri.jp/article/411]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537004971,
      "updated": 1537004974
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd42daff09e00007aad2d",
      "text": "\t\t 個人と組織を同じ方向に進ませるための[動機付け]のフレームワーク",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537004589,
      "updated": 1537004983
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd420aff09e00007aad2b",
      "text": " \t\tグーグルのように、「皆がやりたいことをやる」タイプの組織では特にこのOKRが有効",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537004576,
      "updated": 1537004975
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd42faff09e00007aad2e",
      "text": "\t\t[src https://tech.nikkeibp.co.jp/atcl/nxt/column/18/00134/050200048/]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537004591,
      "updated": 1537004853
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd535aff09e00007aad2f",
      "text": "  \t>O（目標、Objective）を1つ、そのOを測定するためのKR（主な結果、Key Results）を3つほど設定し、その実現に向かって組織と個人が努力する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537004853,
      "updated": 1537004934
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd575aff09e00007aad31",
      "text": "  　>OやKRは、達成する自信が50％くらいの困難なゴールにします。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537004918,
      "updated": 1537004945
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd590aff09e00007aad33",
      "text": "   \t>その代わり、従業員が「達成できたらいいな」と思えるようなワクワクすることを選びます。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537004945,
      "updated": 1537004950
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd596aff09e00007aad34",
      "text": "   >まず企業としてのOKRを設定し、それを受けて部門ごとにも「部門OKR」を作ります。また、定期的に達成具合を振り返り、Oの実現度合いがどれくらい高まっているかをメンバーで確認します。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537004950,
      "updated": 1537004951
    },
    {
      "id": "5b9cd418aff09e00007aad29",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537004569,
      "updated": 1537004591
    }
  ]
}